  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Partner -- No Experience Needed",
  "description": "<p>In today's world, where digital communications dominate, we recognize that face-to-face sales are a crucial part of the marketing mix, providing a personalized and memorable experience for customers. Our services help our clients to introduce, advertise, sell and activate their products or brand through face-to-face marketing, enabling them to stand out in a crowded market and connect with customers in a more impactful way.<br /></p><p>Our clients come from a diverse range of industries, including telecommunications, pay TV, broadband, insurance, consumer products, transport, financial services, technology, fundraising, lifestyle, and energy, and we bring a wealth of experience and knowledge to each project.<br /></p><p><u><strong>The Role</strong></u></p><ul><li>Promote our client products to customers thru different platforms</li><li>Spearhead new campaigns and build your legacy</li><li>Train and build your team in your way, with supports along the way </li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Age 18 and above</li><li>Ready to make a difference by putting in effort and hardworking (No get rich gimmicks)</li><li>Strong learning attitude and accountability in the things you do</li></ul><p><u><strong>Want to know more?</strong></u><br />Apply now or simply drop a WhatsApp to @ 88083166 with your name, age and nationality and we will get back to you at the soonest.</p>",
